Real Madrid face rivals Atletico Madrid in the Champions League quarter-final second leg on Wednesday . 
  Carlo Ancelotti's side drew 0-0 at home in the first leg last week . 
  Cristiano Ronaldo and Co trained ahead of the clash at their Valdebebas base . 
  Dani Carvajal and Co played a small-sided game during the session . 
  Karim Benzema will miss the game through injury . 
  Gareth Bale and Luka Modric are also out for Real Madrid . 
 